==性別和種族==
[[File:Vietnam_Vets_MC_colors.JPG|thumb]]
大多數機車幫會都不允許女性成為正式成員<ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=vWQmx84lZeIC&pg=PA133&lpg=PA133&dq=role+of+women+outlaw+motorcycle+gangs&source=bl&ots=ug9jSGrib-&sig=qCnD8kn2R4RYuRp_LNRs6iMTGso&hl=en&ei=AKjwSfjcMJW-M6_GxakP&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=3#PPA133,M1] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=vWQmx84lZeIC&pg=PA133&lpg=PA133&dq=role+of+women+outlaw+motorcycle+gangs&source=bl&ots=ug9jSGrib-&sig=qCnD8kn2R4RYuRp_LNRs6iMTGso&hl=en&ei=AKjwSfjcMJW-M6_GxakP&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=3#PPA133,M1 |date=20200806001026 }} Book, Organised Crime By Alan Wright</ref>。在機車幫會中，女性是男性成員的服從者<ref>[http://www.ncjrs.gov/App/publications/Abstract.aspx?id=151025] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ncjrs.gov/App/publications/Abstract.aspx?id=151025 |date=20201029112508 }} "Women in Outlaw Motorcycle Clubs," from ''Constructions of Deviance: Social Power, Context, and Interaction'', p. 389-401, 1994, Patricia A and Peter Adler, eds.</ref>，她們被視為幫會財產，被迫賣淫或街頭販毒，經常遭到肉體虐待和性虐待<ref>[http://www.faculty.missouristate.edu/M/MichaelCarlie/Storage/motorcycle_gangs.htm] {{Wayback|url=http://www.faculty.missouristate.edu/M/MichaelCarlie/Storage/motorcycle_gangs.htm |date=20100305054803 }} ''Into the Abyss: A Personal Journey into the World of Street Gangs'', Mike Carlie PhD</ref>，她們的角色是順服成員、追隨成員和交往對象。這些女子被要求將她們收到的任何款項交給她們所屬的成員，有時是交給幫會<ref>[http://jce.sagepub.com/cgi/content/abstract/18/4/363] {{Wayback|url=http://jce.sagepub.com/cgi/content/abstract/18/4/363 |date=20081012070113 }} Journal of Contemporary Ethnography, Vol. 18, No. 4, 363-387 (1990)</ref>，這顯示機車幫會中實行群體性別隔離<ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=Mx-5je_EYAQC&pg=PA149&lpg=PA149&dq=role+of+women+outlaw+motorcycle+gangs&source=bl&ots=_YjlY28SqE&sig=llRAMPaywDdEj5EmBHPJMxVm9aM&hl=en&ei=QqTwSdy6PJjKMOf3zbwP&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=8#PPA150,M1] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Mx-5je_EYAQC&pg=PA149&lpg=PA149&dq=role+of+women+outlaw+motorcycle+gangs&source=bl&ots=_YjlY28SqE&sig=llRAMPaywDdEj5EmBHPJMxVm9aM&hl=en&ei=QqTwSdy6PJjKMOf3zbwP&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=8#PPA150,M1 |date=20200801072616 }} Book, ''Beyond the Mafia'' by Sue Mahan and Katherine O'Neil</ref>，她們是服從[[工人階級|工人階級]]的女子，作為俱樂部和幫會的性儀式對象，即[[妓女|妓女]]、赤裸上身的女招待、脫衣舞者或「賺錢機器」，她們以這些服務來維生並交換幫會的保護<ref>Hopper, C. B., & Moore, J. (1990). Women in outlaw motorcycle gangs. {{link-en|Journal of Contemporary Ethnography|Journal of Contemporary Ethnography}}, 第18章, 第363- 387頁.</ref>。一份1990年的研究文件指出，女性在機車幫會中的作用一直在變化中<ref>Women In Outlaw Motorcycle Gangs. Hopper, Columbus B. And Moore, Johnny. {{link-en|Journal of Contemporary Ethnography|Journal of Contemporary Ethnography}},第18章, 第363- 387頁.</ref>。2000年的一篇研究文章表示，她們現在具有代理人資格和政治頭腦，並重新定義了她們的生活方式：「我們做到了，我們向男人展示了女性的優勢，我更喜歡和一個幫會成員一起生活，而不是像白癡一樣當個系統中的棋子」，這位匿名女子感到她和她的同伴已經改變了不平等狀況<ref>Rappaport, J. (2000). Community narratives: Tales of terror and joy. {{link-en|Journal of Contemporary Ethnography|Journal of Contemporary Ethnography}}, 第28章, 第1-24頁.</ref>。2001年，一名女性描述了以前在機車幫會的世界中，必須成為某位成員的穩定伴侶（Old Lady），生活狀況與地位才會改善<ref name="monash">Depicting outlaw motorcycle club women using anchored and unanchored research methodologies. van den Eynde, [[昆士蘭大學|昆士蘭大學]], Australia and Veno, [[蒙納許大學|蒙納許大學]]</ref><ref name="HotCars3"/>，她們是機車幫會環境的一部分，因為這是一種互利共生的關係。而且這些女性已經破壞了社會定型的角色，並且與機車騎士一樣愛好自由<ref>Joan, Barbara. Bike Lust: Harleys, Women, And American Society. {{link-en|University of Wisconsin Press|University of Wisconsin Press}}, 2001</ref>。但是這種情形並非總是如此，例如在1950年代至1960年代期間，一些[[地獄天使_(幫會)|地獄天使]]的分會中便有女性成員<ref>Ralph (Sonny) Barger. ''Hells Angel''. [[哈珀柯林斯|哈潑柯林斯]], 2001. 第103頁</ref>。

機車幫會反映了他們的社會根源和一般機車騎士的人口統計不同。高調的機車幫會成員一直都是[[白人|白人]]，他們的幫會內部也通常都是白人<ref name=Barker2005>{{Citation |title=One Percent Biker Clubs -- A Description |last=Barker |first=Tom |periodical=Trends in Organized Crime |publisher=Springer New York |issn=1084-4791 |volume=9 |issue= 1 |date=September 2005 |doi=10.1007/s12117-005-1005-0 |page=第111頁 |quote=One percent biker clubs in the existing literature have been described as all white clubs, but there are at least four black or interracial 1% biker clubs.}}</ref>。其他消息來源表明，除了少數例外和[[黑人|黑人]]自行成立的機車幫會，黑人是不能加入白人機車幫會的<ref name="Barker2010">{{cite book|last=Barker|first=Thomas|title=Biker Gangs and Organized Crime|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=pg28hmWc_4wC&pg=PA52|date=2010-04-06|publisher=[[羅德里奇|羅德里奇]]|isbn=978-1-4377-5507-7|page=第52頁|access-date=2017-06-29|archive-date=2020-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200705063156/https://books.google.com/books?id=pg28hmWc_4wC&pg=PA52|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據學術研究，機車幫會成員的平均年齡是34歲<ref>{{Citation |last1=Hopper |first1=Columbus B. |last2=Moore |first2=Johnny "Big John" |title=Hell on Wheels; The Outlaw Motorcycle Gangs |location=Bowling Green, Ohio |periodical=Journal of American Culture |volume=6 |issue=2 |date=Summer 1983 |pages=第58–59頁 |quote=Outlaw cyclists are generally male and between 21 and 45 years of age.}}</ref>。除了白人和黑人，機車幫會的種族也有[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]和其他[[西班牙語|西班牙語]]系的族群<ref>(Killinger and Cromwell, 1978). |doi=10.1111/j.1542-734X.1983.0602_58.x</ref><ref>[http://www.ozbiker.org/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=295&Itemid=35 Outlaw Motorcycle Gangs] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ozbiker.org/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=295&Itemid=35 |date=20200105091021 }}- OZBiker.org</ref>。但是在現今，種族問題似乎已經不像幫會忠誠或幫會哲學對他們那般重要，幾乎所有機車幫會都有兩種以上的膚色了<ref>[http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/27296867 Dozens of outlaw bikers arrested in ATF sting] {{Wayback|url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/27296867 |date=20121231042320 }}- [[MSNBC|MSNBC]], 2008-10-21</ref>。據稱，一些非白人騎士被當地的[[地獄天使_(幫會)|地獄天使]]分會拒絕加入後，地獄天使內堅持的種族歧視已經導致這些人加入敵對幫會，使對手勢力逐漸壯大，例如{{link-en|蒙古機車俱樂部|Mongols Motorcycle Club|蒙古幫}}<ref>[http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/27296867 Dozens of Outlaw Bikers Arrested in ATF Sting.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/27296867 |date=20121231042320 }}- [[MSNBC|MSNBC]], 2008-10-21</ref>。一些機車幫會和底下的分會現在是多種族，但懷有[[白人優越主義|白人優越主義]]的機車幫會正在美國全境範圍內增長<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.adl.org/press-center/press-releases/extremism/report-white-supremacist.html|publisher=[[反誹謗聯盟|反誹謗聯盟]]|title="White Supremacist Biker Clubs Are Growing Nationwide"|accessdate=2017-06-29|archive-date=2016-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161018220417/http://www.adl.org/press-center/press-releases/extremism/report-white-supremacist.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.adl.org/combating-hate/domestic-extremism-terrorism/c/bigots-on-bikes.html#.U7rh4ChsE24|title="Bigots on Bikes: The Growing Links between White Supremacists and Biker Gangs"|publisher=[[反誹謗聯盟|反誹謗聯盟]]|accessdate=2017-06-29|archive-date=2017-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170105200040/http://www.adl.org/combating-hate/domestic-extremism-terrorism/c/bigots-on-bikes.html#.U7rh4ChsE24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==犯罪行為==
一些機車幫會成員從事[[犯罪|犯罪]]和[[組織犯罪|有組織犯罪]]活動<ref name=USDOJ_Motorcycle_Gangs1>{{Citation |title=Motorcycle Gangs |url=http://www.justice.gov/criminal/gangunit/gangs/motorcycle.html |author=[[美國司法部|美國司法部]] |accessdate=2009-10-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100210150226/http://www.justice.gov/criminal/gangunit/gangs/motorcycle.html |archivedate=2010-02-10 }}</ref>。儘管與機車和「1%」次文化有關，執法機構認為這些個人和機車幫會在犯罪集團的類型中是獨一無二的，因為他們會維護網站和事業形象，透過布章和紋身來識別自己和他人，制定並遵守律法和章程、商標、幫會名稱和標誌，甚至舉行為了改善公眾形象的宣傳活動<ref name=Adler2001>{{Citation |title=The Fall of a Hells Angel Leader; Indictment Alleges Spokesman's Charity Masks Drug Ring. |first=Jeff |last= Adler |newspaper=[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]] |location= [[華盛頓特區|華盛頓特區]] |date= 2001-03-03 |page=第A.07頁}}</ref><ref name=Barker2005/>。

===犯罪事業===
[[File:Gypsy_Joker_Protest_Run_8.jpg|thumb]]一個機車幫派抗議遊行的聚集場景。]]
[[美國司法部|美國司法部]]將「不法機車幫派」（Outlaw Motorcycle Gang）定義為「成員使用機車俱樂部作為犯罪企業渠道」的[[掩護機構|掩護組織]]<ref name=USDOJ_Motorcycle_Gangs2>{{Citation |title=Motorcycle Gangs |url=http://www.justice.gov/criminal/ocgs/gangs/motorcycle.html |author=[[美國司法部|美國司法部]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140415074158/http://www.justice.gov/criminal/ocgs/gangs/motorcycle.html |archivedate=2014-04-15 |accessdate=2017-06-29 }}</ref>。美國[[聯邦調查局|聯邦調查局]]和{{link-en|加拿大刑事情報局|Criminal Intelligence Service Canada}}已經將一些機車俱樂部列為「不法機車幫派」，例如[[地獄天使_(幫會)|地獄天使]]、{{link-en|異教徒機車俱樂部|Pagan's Motorcycle Club|異教徒}}、{{link-en|亡命之徒機車俱樂部|Outlaws Motorcycle Club|亡命之徒}}和{{link-en|惡棍之徒機車俱樂部|Bandidos Motorcycle Club|惡棍之徒}}<ref>[http://pdba.georgetown.edu/Security/citizensecurity/eeuu/documents/ssgu00.pdf FBI Safe Street Violent Crime Initiative - Report Fiscal Year 2000] {{Wayback|url=http://pdba.georgetown.edu/Security/citizensecurity/eeuu/documents/ssgu00.pdf |date=20200924090258 }}- [[聯邦調查局|聯邦調查局]]</ref><ref>[http://www.cisc.gc.ca/annual_reports/annual_report_2004/document/cisc_2004_annual_report.pdf 2004 Annual Report] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cisc.gc.ca/annual_reports/annual_report_2004/document/cisc_2004_annual_report.pdf |date=20091222072041 }}- {{link-en|加拿大刑事情報局|Criminal Intelligence Service Canada}}, cisc.gc.ca</ref>，它們被稱為「機車幫會四巨頭」<ref>[http://ctgia.org/mcgang.html Motorcycle Gangs] {{Wayback|url=http://ctgia.org/mcgang.html |date=20150804054924 }}- Connecticut Gang Investigators Association</ref>。這四個幫會擁有足夠大的全國性影響，能應對《{{link-en|美國反詐欺和腐敗組織法案|Racketeer Influenced and Corrupt Organizations Act}}》的章程<ref>[http://www.cisc.gc.ca/annual_reports/annual_report_2004/document/cisc_2004_annual_report.pdf 2004 Annual Report] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cisc.gc.ca/annual_reports/annual_report_2004/document/cisc_2004_annual_report.pdf |date=20091222072041 }}- {{link-en|加拿大刑事情報局|Criminal Intelligence Service Canada}} (CISC), cisc.gc.ca</ref>。{{link-en|加州總檢察長|Attorney General of California}}也將{{link-en|蒙古機車俱樂部|Mongols Motorcycle Club|蒙古幫}}和{{link-en|浪子機車俱樂部|Vagos Motorcycle Club|浪子幫}}列為「不法機車幫派」<ref>[http://ag.ca.gov/publications/org_crime2004.pdf Organized Crime in California - 2004 Annual Report to the Legislature] {{Wayback|url=http://ag.ca.gov/publications/org_crime2004.pdf |date=20110912192103 }}- {{link-en|加利福尼亞州司法部|California Department of Justice}}</ref><ref>[http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/27296867/ Dozens of outlaw bikers arrested in [[美國菸酒槍炮及爆裂物管理局|ATF]] sting] {{Wayback|url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/27296867/ |date=20121231042320 }}- [[MSNBC|MSNBC]] 2008-10-21</ref>。

聯邦調查局稱，「不法機車幫派」主要透過[[毒品|毒品]]交易、販運贓物和敲詐勒索來維生，並且他們還參與區域勢力和非法毒品交易鬥爭當中<ref>[http://www.apsu.edu/oconnort/3220/3220lect07a.htm Organized Crime Investigation] {{Wayback|url=http://www.apsu.edu/oconnort/3220/3220lect07a.htm |date=20070206090126 }}- by T. O'Connor, [[奧斯汀佩伊州立大學|奧斯汀佩伊州立大學]]</ref>，每年的獲取的金額約為十億美元<ref>[http://money.cnn.com/magazines/fortune/fortune_archive/1992/11/30/77184/index.htm The Hells Angels' Devilish Business] {{Wayback|url=http://money.cnn.com/magazines/fortune/fortune_archive/1992/11/30/77184/index.htm |date=20191203053949 }}- [[CNN|CNN]] 1992-11-30</ref><ref>[http://www.cbc.ca/news/background/bikergangs/ Biker Gangs in Canada] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/background/bikergangs/ |date=20040603002852 }}- {{link-en|加拿大廣播公司新聞|CBC News}}, 2007-04-05</ref><ref>[http://www.nationalgangcenter.gov/news/2005_10_04_NDW_Vol_4_No_40_Gangs.pdf Narcotics Digest, Gangs In The United States] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nationalgangcenter.gov/news/2005_10_04_NDW_Vol_4_No_40_Gangs.pdf |date=20090325153857 }}- {{link-en|全國幫派情報中心|National Gang Intelligence Center}}</ref><ref>[http://www.dea.gov/speeches/s102005.html Comprehensively Combating Methamphetamine: Impact on Health and the Environment] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dea.gov/speeches/s102005.html |date=20080516211618 }}- [[美國緝毒局|美國緝毒局]] Deputy Chief Joseph Rannazzisi, congressional testimony on 2005-10-20</ref><ref>[http://money.cnn.com/magazines/fortune/fortune_archive/1992/11/30/77184/index.htm The Hells Angels' Devilish Business] {{Wayback|url=http://money.cnn.com/magazines/fortune/fortune_archive/1992/11/30/77184/index.htm |date=20191203053949 }}- by Andrew E. Serwer, [[財星_(雜誌)|財星 (雜誌)]], 1992-11-30</ref><ref name=Barger>[http://www.phoenixnewtimes.com/1992-12-02/news/look-homeward-angelcycle-icon-sonny-barger-kick-starts-life-as-a-free-man-by-violating-parole/ Look Homeward Angel: Cycle Icon Sonny Barger Kick-Starts Life as a Free Man by Violating Parole] {{Wayback|url=http://www.phoenixnewtimes.com/1992-12-02/news/look-homeward-angelcycle-icon-sonny-barger-kick-starts-life-as-a-free-man-by-violating-parole/ |date=20150405163203 }}- by Philip Martin, {{link-en|Phoenix New Times|Phoenix New Times}}, 1992-12-02</ref>。1985年，聯邦調查局破獲了一次歷來最大的不法機車幫派，沒收了兩百萬美元的非法毒品和非法武器庫，包括[[烏茲衝鋒槍|烏茲衝鋒槍]]和[[反坦克武器|反坦克武器]]<ref name=Barger/><ref>[http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,968213,00.html Busting Hell's Angels] {{Wayback|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,968213,00.html |date=20130822233601 }}- [[時代_(雜誌)|時代 (雜誌)]], 1985-05-13</ref>。2008年10月，聯邦調查局宣布結束六個月的秘密行動，由特務幹員進入蒙古幫臥底，最終下達了160份搜查令和110份逮捕令，破獲該幫會的[[麻醉藥品|麻醉藥品]]走私販運<ref>[http://www.kval.com/news/31724039.html Feds bust motorcycle gang with Ore. ties] {{Wayback|url=http://www.kval.com/news/31724039.html |date=20090714132750 }} - {{link-en|KVAL-CBS|KVAL-TV}}, 2008-10-21</ref>。

在[[加拿大|加拿大]]，特別是在[[20世纪|20世纪]]末期，機車幫會的犯罪案件大量增加，其中最著名的是{{link-en|魁北克車手之戰|Quebec Biker war}}，那場暴力地盤爭奪戰導致約150人死亡，包括一位無辜的旁觀者被汽車炸彈炸死<ref>[http://observer.guardian.co.uk/uk_news/story/0,6903,382689,00.html Was Noye case witness killed by Hell's Angels?]- [[衛報|衛報]], 2000-10-15</ref><ref name="Organized Crime Fact Sheet"/>。加拿大的暴力事件增加歸因於非法販毒業務進入{{link-en|蒙特婁港|Port of Montreal}}，引起幫會地盤的戰爭<ref>''The Biker Trials: Bringing Down the Hells Angels'', by Paul Cherry, {{link-en|ECW Press|ECW Press}}, 2005</ref>，而且地獄天使也試圖從加拿大各地的對手或獨立幫派中獲取街頭貿易的控制權<ref>''Fallen Angel: The Unlikely Rise of Walter Stadnick in the Canadian Hells Angels'', by Jerry Langton, Wiley & Sons, 2006</ref> 根據[[皇家加拿大騎警|皇家加拿大騎警]]在{{link-en|曼尼托巴省法院|Provincial Court of Manitoba}}的公報中，他們將這些團體定義為「任一集團的機車愛好者，自願作出承諾、聯合起來，以暴力強制遵循他們組織的嚴格規則，從事與社會和法律嚴重衝突的活動」<ref name="Organized Crime Fact Sheet">[http://ww2.ps-sp.gc.ca/policing/organized_crime/FactSheets/omg_e.asp Organized Crime Fact Sheet] {{Wayback|url=http://ww2.ps-sp.gc.ca/policing/organized_crime/FactSheets/omg_e.asp |date=20081018195221 }}- [[加拿大公共安全部|加拿大公共安全部]]</ref>。這些分會的成員和支持者堅持認為非法活動是孤立的事件，而且整個非法行為並不是有組織犯罪，機車俱樂部也不是犯罪組織。他們經常將自己與警察部門進行比較，其中一小部分的「壞警察」並不會使整個警察部門成為犯罪組織，而地獄天使則是贊助捐助活動的公益慈善組織<ref>[http://www.missoulian.com/specials/hellsangels/ha01.html Storm Approaching] {{Wayback|url=http://www.missoulian.com/specials/hellsangels/ha01.html |date=20090510143450 }}- by Michael Jamison, {{link-en|Missoulian|Missoulian}}, July 2000</ref>。

與其他犯罪組織相反，機車幫會以個人為基礎，而不是自上而下的科層制度，支持者可以聲稱只有一些成員犯罪，每個成員都可以自行選擇從事的活動，並和[[黑手黨|黑手黨]]等其他犯罪組織的「不道德的家庭主義」層級秩序和命令相比較，機車幫會的性質只是「不道德的個人主義」<ref>[http://www.tandemnews.com/printer.php?storyid=96] {{Wayback|url=http://www.tandemnews.com/printer.php?storyid=96 |date=20090706022430 }} Tandem News, Angels With Dirty Faces by Antonio Nicaso</ref>。[[美國菸酒槍炮及爆裂物管理局|美國菸酒槍炮及爆裂物管理局]]探員{{link-en|威廉·昆恩|William Queen}}曾滲入蒙古幫臥底，他表示機車幫會不像[[黑社會|黑社會]]這樣的組織，犯罪和暴力的目的不是用來追求利潤的手段，而是追求某種生活哲學，混亂和無法無天是機車幫會成員的生活方式，他們透過非法手段獲得金錢，只是一種維持生計的手段<ref>{{Citation |author={{link-en|威廉·昆恩|William Queen}} |title=Under and Alone: The True Story of the Undercover Agent Who Infiltrated America's Most Violent Outlaw Motorcycle Gang |publisher=[[藍燈書屋|藍燈書屋]] |year=2006 |isbn=0-345-48752-4 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=s85YVXxHZgIC&pg=PA65 |page=第65頁 |accessdate=2017-06-29 |archive-date=2020-08-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805005324/https://books.google.com/books?id=s85YVXxHZgIC&pg=PA65 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

近來許多國家的政府部門已經嘗試破壞機車幫會和瓦解成員資格的制度。2011年6月，[[澳洲高等法院|澳洲高等法院]]推翻了一項法律，禁止以犯罪為重點的機車俱樂部存在，並要求成員們避免彼此接觸<ref name=Godfrey2011>{{Citation |newspaper= [[雪梨晨鋒報|雪梨晨鋒報]] |title= Hells Angel kills NSW anti-bikie laws |first= Miles |last= Godfrey |date= 2011-06-23 |accessdate= 2011-06-23 |url= http://news.smh.com.au/breaking-news-national/hells-angel-kills-nsw-antibikie-laws-20110623-1ggao.html |archive-date= 2014-03-26 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140326170343/http://news.smh.com.au/breaking-news-national/hells-angel-kills-nsw-antibikie-laws-20110623-1ggao.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。在美國，一名[[美國聯邦法官|聯邦法官]]駁回了檢察機關要求奪取蒙古幫的幫會標誌和名稱所有權，稱政府沒有該[[商標|商標]]的持有權<ref name=Risling2011>{{Citation |title= Judge sides with biker gang over logo |first1= Greg |url= http://www.mercurynews.com/news/ci_18420209 |accessdate=2011-07-07 |last= Risling |newspaper=[[聖荷西信使報|聖荷西信使報]] |publisher= [[美聯社|美聯社]]}}</ref><ref name=Clough2011>{{Citation |title= Judge Rejects Government Attempt to Seize Mongols Biker Gang's 'Colors'; The U.S. Attorney's Office says the effort marks the first time in which the government has sought a gang's trademarks |first= Craig |last= Clough |newspaper= {{link-en|North Hollywood and Toluca Lake Patch|North Hollywood and Toluca Lake Patch}} |url= http://northhollywood.patch.com/articles/judge-rejects-government-attempt-to-seize-mongols-biker-gangs-colors |accessdate= 2011-07-07 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20110713025330/http://northhollywood.patch.com/articles/judge-rejects-government-attempt-to-seize-mongols-biker-gangs-colors |archivedate= 2011-07-13 }}</ref>。聯邦[[檢察官|檢察官]]也曾起草更大的刑事起訴書，要求提供政府對該標誌所有權的法院命令，以防止機車幫會成員穿戴幫派背心<ref name=Mather2011>{{Citation |first= Kate |last= Mather |title= Feds want to bar Mongols biker gang from using its trademarked logo |date= 2011-06-20 |newspaper= [[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]] |accessdate= 2011-06-23 |url= http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/lanow/2011/06/feds-wants-to-bar-mongols-biker-gang-from-trademarking-its-logo-.html |archive-date= 2020-11-12 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201112040403/https://latimesblogs.latimes.com/lanow/2011/06/feds-wants-to-bar-mongols-biker-gang-from-trademarking-its-logo-.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

==機車幫會之間的關係==
某些大型機車幫會相互競爭，通常是在領土問題、生意範圍和其他問題進行鬥爭。有時，勢力較小的機車幫會被迫或自願協助成為另一個更大的機車幫會，有時需要在他們的背心縫上一個「支援布章」，表明他們與主導地區事務的機車幫會有聯繫。一般情況下，主導地區事務的機車幫會允許較小的幫會存在並交易牟利。另一些被抵制、不被允許的俱樂部會遭到威脅、侵略、攻擊或強行解散<ref>[http://www.reviewjournal.com/lvrj_home/2006/Oct-05-Thu-2006/news/10051829.html Ex-Hells Angels official says cops kept out of club] {{Wayback|url=http://www.reviewjournal.com/lvrj_home/2006/Oct-05-Thu-2006/news/10051829.html |date=20121122025856 }}- by Adrienne Packer, {{link-en|Las Vegas Review-Journal|Las Vegas Review-Journal}}, 2006-10-05</ref><ref>[http://www.reviewjournal.com/lvrj_home/2002/Apr-30-Tue-2002/news/18638909.html Laughlin Shootout: Signs told of melee in making] {{Wayback|url=http://www.reviewjournal.com/lvrj_home/2002/Apr-30-Tue-2002/news/18638909.html |date=20110920073433 }}- by Glenn Puit and Dave Berns, {{link-en|Las Vegas Review-Journal|Las Vegas Review-Journal}}, 2002-04-30</ref><ref>[https://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9C0DE0DA1239F930A25750C0A9649C8B63 73 Bikers Arrested] {{Wayback|url=https://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9C0DE0DA1239F930A25750C0A9649C8B63 |date=20100922073601 }}- [[紐約時報|紐約時報]], 2002-03-13</ref>。

在[[澳洲|澳洲]]<ref>[http://www.abc.net.au/am/content/2012/s3492444.htm Diverse groups unite to fight anti-association laws] {{Wayback|url=http://www.abc.net.au/am/content/2012/s3492444.htm |date=20170827121725 }}. David Weber, {{link-en|ABC News Australia|ABC News (Australia)}}</ref>和美國，許多機車幫會已經建立了廣布全國的幫派聯盟<ref name="ball" />，這些聯盟由擁有州級堂口的幫會成員和偶爾參與的第三方組織組合而成，定期召開會議，每個機車幫會派出成員代表解決幫會之間的爭議，並討論共同關心的議題或利益。地區性聯盟或幫派聯盟已經平息了一些幫會之間的競爭和衝突局勢，並且他們還一同僱用法律顧問和公關代表<ref name="ball">Terry the Tramp: The Life and Dangerous Times of a One Percenter. K. Randall Ball. MotorBooks International, 2011-10-30</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/features/ferrets-manifesto/story-e6frg8h6-1225894609789 |title=Ferret's manifesto. RICHARD GUILLIATT. The Australian 2010-07-20 |publisher=[[澳洲人報|澳洲人報]] |date=2013-08-29 |accessdate=2013-11-12 |archive-date=2014-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140412105905/http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/features/ferrets-manifesto/story-e6frg8h6-1225894609789 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==文化影響==
不法騎士及其機車幫會經常在電影和媒體中被廣泛描繪或模仿，形成了{{link-en|不法騎士電影|Outlaw biker film}}類型<ref>Two Wheels on Two Reels: A History of Biker Movies. Mike Seate. Whitehorse Press, 2000-12-24</ref>，它通常以公眾潛意識中的負面刻板印象存在<ref>At the Movies, Strandberg, Keith. {{link-en|American Motorcyclist|American Motorcyclist}}, Oct 1987</ref>，並激盪出[[時裝|時裝]]流行趨勢<ref>The Dictionary of Fashion History. Valerie Cumming, C. W. Cunnington, P. E. Cunnington. Berg, 2010-11-15</ref><ref>Harley-Davidson and Philosophy: Full-Throttle Aristotle. Bernard E. Rollin. {{link-en|Open Court Publishing Company|Open Court Publishing Company}}, 2006-02-09</ref><ref>The Rebels: A Brotherhood of Outlaw Bikers. Daniel R. Wolf. {{link-en|University of Toronto Press|University of Toronto Press}}, 1991</ref>，包括男性的豪邁氣概和性感女騎士的時尚形象<ref>Consumers. Eric J. Arnould, Linda Price, George Martin Zinkhan. {{link-en|McGraw-Hill/Irwin|McGraw-Hill Education}}, 2004</ref><ref>《[[Elle|Elle]]》, Issues 273-275. [[ELLE|Elle Publishing Company]], 2008</ref><ref>The House of Klein: Fashion, Controversy, and a Business Obsession. Lisa Marsh. [[約翰威立|約翰威立]], 2003-08-18</ref>。這甚至引起一些機車幫會和時裝公司針對服飾上的法律糾紛<ref>'Hells Angels sue luxury fashion house'. Brichall, Jonathan. [[金融時報|金融時報]], 2010-10-27 [http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/caf87e7a-e153-11df-90b7-00144feabdc0.html#axzz1xBrfaPXA] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/caf87e7a-e153-11df-90b7-00144feabdc0.html#axzz1xBrfaPXA |date=20101030023827 }}</ref>，同時廣泛傳達了危險、叛逆、陽剛之氣和[[工人階級|工人階級]]的價值觀<ref name="Wojcik" />。

機車幫會和不法騎士的衣著風格和生活方式影響了其他次文化，例如[[龐克文化|龐克文化]]<ref name="Wojcik">Punk and Neo-Tribal Body Art. Daniel Wojcik. {{link-en|University Press of Mississippi|University Press of Mississippi}}, 1995</ref>、[[重金屬音樂|重金屬音樂]]<ref>David Muggleton、Rupert Weinzierl《The Post-Subcultures Reader》{{link-en|Berg Publishers|Berg Publishers}}（2003-12-01）ISBN 978-1859736685.[2004-04-17]</ref>、[[皮革次文化|皮革次文化]]<ref>Movie-made America: a cultural history of American movies. Robert Sklar. [[Vintage_Books|Vintage Books]], 1994</ref>、[[哥德次文化|哥德次文化]]和{{link-en|數位歌德|cybergoth}}時尚<ref>As Seen in Vogue: A Century of American Fashion in Advertising. Daniel Delis Hill. {{link-en|Texas Tech University Press|Texas Tech University Press}}, 2007-09-15</ref>。特別是在重金屬音樂的文化圈中，由幫會背心演變出來的[[金屬戰袍|金屬戰袍]]也已經成為一種服飾風格，成為樂迷表達個性、音樂品味和歸屬感的一種方式，衣物上的布章、補丁和徽章都由樂團標誌、專輯封面或其他藝術品取而代之<ref name="homeofmetal">{{cite web|publisher=homeofmetal|url=https://homeofmetal.com/battle-jackets-rebellion-creativity-and-devotion/|title=BATTLE JACKETS: REBELLION, CREATIVITY AND DEVOTION|accessdate=2020-06-27|date=2017-04-25|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115212155/https://homeofmetal.com/battle-jackets-rebellion-creativity-and-devotion/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|title=Handbook of Police Administration |author=Hummer, Don |page= 276}}</ref>。機車幫會最初是一個美國人的次文化，現今已具有國際影響力<ref>The Berg Companion to Fashion. Valerie Steele. {{link-en|Berg Publishers|Berg Publishers}}, 2010-11-15</ref>，重機騎士的衣服和機車已經成為一種文化象徵<ref>Mobility Without Mayhem: Safety, Cars, and Citizenship. Jeremy Packer. {{link-en|Duke University Press|Duke University Press}}, 2008-02-05</ref><ref>Profane Culture. Paul E. Willis. Taylor & Francis, 1978</ref>，他們的地位和形象普遍受到媒體誇大或[[神化|神化]]<ref>Framing Public Life: Perspectives on Media and Our Understanding of the Social World. Stephen D. Reese, Oscar H. Gandy, August E. Grant. [[羅德里奇|羅德里奇]], 2003-06-01</ref>。

